# Index Page Theme – Do Not Modify

- **Never change, remove, or replace** the Aura pastel teal + blue orbs theme on the index page.
- The theme lives in **index.html** only: the inline `<style>` block and the `.orb-layer` div with orbs (classes `ot1`–`ot9`, `ob1`–`ob8`). Do not edit that block except for critical bugs.
- In **assets/css/main.css**: **Do not add** any rules that affect the index page background or theme, including:
  - `body.index-page` background, `body.index-page::before`, or any `::before`/`::after` overlay for the index page
  - Any gradient, animated background, or “floating”/“orb” styles in main.css for the index page
- The index page must keep: white/light background, pastel teal + blue orbs, frosted header, transparent sections. No dark overlays or competing backgrounds.
- **Section headers**: To change section titles/labels, only edit (1) the section header HTML in each `<section>` and (2) the `<style id="section-headers-styles">` block in index.html. Do not add theme, background, body, or ::before in that block. Do not add index-page background/overlay rules in main.css.
